cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image feature extraction and matching for camera localization. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper proposes a method for camera pose estimation in 3D point clouds, which is relevant to robotics applications. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a Descriptor-Matcher algorithm that is trained on a dataset of matching 2D and 3D descriptors. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for camera localization that involves machine learning techniques. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with matching image features with 3D point cloud descriptors, which is relevant to computer graphics applications.
